Hey everyone,
We are currently pursuing an exciting off-season project which requires a lot of Kraken motors (both X44 and X60). Sadly, our current in-shop stock will not get us there…

We planned on purchasing those from WCP/CTRE but sadly they are out of stock.

Does anyone by any chance know when these motors are expected to be restocked?
Are there any teams who would be open to sell them?

Thanks in advance,
MisCar 1574
